      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JALAPENO GEM (2) has a strong overall record having 10 wins and 23 places from 50 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (30.10) over 512m at Mt Gambier. Form here sound including three wins. Expected to feature in the finish. PAW EVA (4) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (30.92) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including two wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Should be about the money. MINNIE'S MY MUM (1) clocked an impressive 22.03 to claim a Grade 3/4/5 over 395m at Murray Bridge last start. Has the ability and looks a key chance. CANYA NAMELESS (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
